            "description": "Create a new residence permit application.\n\nIMPORTANT: If the submission_deadline is within 30 days, the service will automatically:\n1. Fetch student name via gRPC from Student Profile Service.\n2. Publish a 'ResidenceDeadlineApproaching' event to RabbitMQ.\n3. Notification Service will send an email + Socket.io alert.\n\nTo test the automatic notification, use a submission_deadline that is within 30 days from today.\nRequires JWT token."
